<p><b>David Crystal</b>, <a href="Order_of_the_British_Empire" title="Order of the British Empire">OBE</a>, <a href="Fellow_of_the_British_Academy" title="Fellow of the British Academy" class="mw-redirect">FBA</a>, <a href="Fellow_of_the_Learned_Society_of_Wales" title="Fellow of the Learned Society of Wales" class="mw-redirect">FLSW</a> (born July 6, 1941) is a <a href="Linguistics" title="Linguistics">linguist</a>, <a href="Academic" title="Academic" class="mw-redirect">academic</a> and <a href="Author" title="Author">author</a>.</p>
